QuestData.Title: Storming the Steamvault
QuestData.Description: We have not as of yet been able to stop the naga in the Steamvault, where most of their pumping infrastructure is located.$B$BThankfully, the expedition I sent there is hard at work trying to change that fact. Will you travel to the Steamvault and offer Watcher Jhang and her crew your aid?
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Watcher Jhang in the Steamvault.
